@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam arrowColor #333333
skinparam sequence {
  LifeLineBorderColor #333333
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
  ParticipantBorderColor #333333
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantPadding 15
}

title LingFlow 认证流程

participant "客户端" as Client
participant "服务端" as Server
database "数据库" as DB

== 1. 获取 Token (REST API) ==

Client -> Server: POST /api/auth/token\n{ user_id, api_key }
Server -> Server: 验证凭证
Server -> DB: 查询用户信息
DB --> Server: 用户信息
Server -> Server: 生成 HMAC Token\nbase64url(userID|exp)\n.hex(hmacSha256)
Server --> Client: { token, expires_at, user_id }

== 2. WebSocket 连接认证 ==

Client -> Server: WS Connect /chat/{uuid}\n?token=xxx\n或 Authorization: Bearer xxx
Server -> Server: 验证 Token 签名
Server -> Server: 验证 Token 过期时间
Server -> Server: Origin 白名单检查
Server -> Server: 单 IP 连接数限制

alt 认证通过
    Server --> Client: 101 Switching Protocols
    Server -> Server: 记录连接事件
    Server --> Client: system_skills_list\n(推送技能列表)
else 认证失败
    Server --> Client: 401 Unauthorized
end

@enduml